	<h1 class="title">日本刚刚允许民宿运营了，它带来什么机会，又遇到怎样的困境？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">胡晓琪</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-17 09:15:30 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25430/medium/25430.jpg?1460554399" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


